{"tid":885911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三國時代黎講 真戰神係張遼囉","createTime":"2018-11-01T16:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T12:34:45.000Z","uid":209890,"like":20,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b588a0015033e57ae832c82d4269a9aa6ef9d038","tid":885911,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:44:59.000Z","msg":"800勇士大破孫權十萬大軍<br />\n雖然九成吹大兵數但係冇十萬點都有二萬喇掛<br />\n將軍帶兵去突襲<br />\n我諗成個中華歷史都無邊個將軍會親自帶兵咁做<br />\n仲要係步兵夜襲大軍 騎士無可能喇因為太嘈<br />\n被包圍 殺出重圍 仲有小量兵被圍 回頭救走佢地 嚇到孫權即刻走佬<br />\n以少勝多仲要大破敵軍贏埋<br />\n斯巴達都係拖得到三日就全軍玩完"},{"pid":"f591d668a03a63004ec8f230a0501fc3a7c7e69f","tid":885911,"uid":4846,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"沒有人可以突破我的劍圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a05df0ae222fb73383d8051285615c5d609857e","tid":885911,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"從來冇人可以突破我的劍圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劍圍張"},{"pid":"1f2d61bd4d960c13c37493c2ccdfe4a252bbdcac","tid":885911,"uid":7916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"好似話係幾乎捉到/搞撚掂孫權<br />\n真係好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02eec5c82afb3ec62ea9905bde6692e8d08e22a8","tid":885911,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2d61bd4d960c13c37493c2ccdfe4a252bbdcac","tid":885911,"uid":7916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"好似話係幾乎捉到/搞撚掂孫權<br />\n真係好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:28:08.000Z","msg":"800人打十萬真係痴線"},{"pid":"0819fb858b3e5824b5361238859a27c11e6e8679","tid":885911,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit